---
const challenges = [
  {
    title: 'Uncertain discounts · Loss of trust',
    description:
      'Discounts and offers often fail to guarantee genuine savings, creating skepticism among students and entrepreneurs about authenticity and value.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Uneven sales · No loyal audience',
    description:
      'Unpredictable turnout leads to erratic cash flow, idle staff, and an inability to forecast inventory with confidence.',
  },
  {
    title: 'High marketing costs · No reach',
    description:
      'Connecting with trustworthy young audiences is expensive and inefficient. Campaigns rarely convert into repeat shoppers.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Deadstock everywhere',
    description:
      'Unsold inventory blocks new product cycles, drains working capital, and fills precious shelf space with stale SKUs.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Zero citywide presence',
    description:
      'Conventional marketing cannot make retail owners visible across the city, so brand equity stays hyperlocal and fragile.',
  },
  {
    title: 'No franchise support',
    description:
      'Without real-time intelligence or agile enablement, scaling to new neighborhoods becomes risky and slow.',
  },
];
---

<section id="challenges" class="relative overflow-hidden bg-night px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-24">
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 opacity-20">
    <div class="h-full w-full bg-[repeating-linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(246,64,64,0.25)_0px,rgba(246,64,64,0.25)_12px,transparent_12px,transparent_32px)]"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-6xl space-y-12">
    <div class="space-y-4 text-center">
      <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-fire/30 bg-fire/10 px-4 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-fire">
        Vendor Advisory
        <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-fire"></span>
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white sm:text-4xl">Challenges vendors face before joining Shievon</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-base text-slate-300">
        These danger zones keep emerging in every conversation with campus retailers, boutique store owners, and indie
        merchants. We surface them boldly so you know exactly what Shievon is built to neutralize.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      {challenges.map((challenge) => (
        <article class="relative rounded-3xl border border-fire/40 bg-black/70 p-6 text-left text-slate-100 shadow-[0_35px_80px_rgba(246,64,64,0.18)]">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-fire/60 bg-fire/10 text-fire">
              !
            </span>
            {/* <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-fire/90">Danger signal</p> */}
            <h3 class="mt-0 text-xl font-semibold text-white">{challenge.title}</h3>
          </div>

          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-300">{challenge.description}</p>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-fire/70">
            <span class="inline-flex h-2 w-8 rounded-full bg-fire/60"></span>
            Addressed by Shievon SRP stack
          </div>
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>